Data.name: CtrlPASSTestRunsExecutedMPT BE
Data.description: tracking the NL boyz for BE

Data.name: CtrlTestsInTestPlanNoEvidence WKL BE
Data.description: All Tests in WKL BE Test Plan without Test Evidence
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND ((issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE', PASS, '', 'true', '', 'false', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'true', 'false')) OR (issue in testExecutionTests('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE', PASS, '', 'false', '', 'false', 'false')))

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlan WKL BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpen WKL BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTDefectsInTestPlanOpenCritical WKL BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in defectsCreatedDuringTestExecution('MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE') AND status not in (Closed, Resolved) AND Priority = critical ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlan WKL BE
Data.jql: project = MILES4ALL AND issue in testPlanTestExecutions('MPTTestPlan WKL BE') ORDER BY rank

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUserPASSNoEvidence WKL BE

Data.name: MPTTestsInTestPlanUnreleasedPASSEvidence WKL BE

Data.name: MPTTestExecsInTestPlanUnreleasedAssignedToCurrentUser WKL BE
Data.description: Executions in Test Plan Unreleased for current User
